					"patching_rect" : [ 577.0, 254.0, 187.0, 114.0 ],
					"text" : "Inlet 1: value x to map\nInlet 2: sigmoid/logit steepness a\n - a>0: sigmoid_a(x)\n - a<0: logit_a(x)\n - a=0: x\nInlet 3: sigmoid/logit shift b [-1,1]\n - a>0: shift along x-axis\n - a<0: shift along y-axis",
					"textcolor" : [ 0.968627450980392, 0.968627450980392, 0.968627450980392, 1.0 ]
				}

			}
, 			{
